# QA Agent

## Priority

1. New API integration tests
2. RBAC/auth CRUD regression
3. Frontend critical flow regression

## Validation

```bash
./gradlew test
cd frontend && npm test
```

## PR Checklist

- [ ] No direct feature commit to `main`
- [ ] Backend and frontend tests passed
- [ ] Ticket scope and diff match
